Package: sensobol
Title: sensobol: an R package to swiftly compute and bootstrap Sobol' sensitivity indices
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Arnald",
           family = "Puy",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "arnald.puy@gmail.com", 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9469-2156"))
Description: It allows to swiftly compute and bootstrap Sobol' first, second, third and 
    total-order effects using the estimators by Saltelli et al. 2010 and 
    Jansen 1999. It also provides support for plotting the results via ggplot2.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
